
@{
    ViewBag.Title = "Tanning";
}

<div class="container">
	<div class="jumbotron">
		<h1>custom airbrush spray tan</h1>
		<img class="img-responsive" style="margin: 0 auto 12px auto;" src="/content/images/fancy-lines-sm.png" alt="Alternate Text" />
		<div class="row" style="margin-top:25px;">

			<div class="col-md-6" style="font-size:medium">
				<p>Spray Tanning is the only way to get a healthy tan.  Avoid the
				risk of skin cancer and premature aging by choosing to get a
				spray tan.  Spray tanning has come a long way.  We use the finest,
				organic solutions that won't leave you with a "tell tale" smell
				and will never turn you <span style="color:#FF9100">orange</span>.
				Your tan will be hand-sprayed with unmatched experience and care,
				guranteeing that you will leave here looking and feeling <span style=
				"color:#BFA452">golden</span>!
				</p>
				<br />
				<p style="font-size:medium; color:rgb(146, 58, 7)"><em><span class="pull-left">one tan - 40</span><span class="pull-right">three tans - 90</span></em></p>
			</div>

			<div class="col-md-5">
				<div class="slider-wrapper theme-default">
					<div class="ribbon"></div>
					<div id="slider" class="nivoSlider">
					    <img src="/content/images/tanning/1.jpg" alt="" />
					    <img src="/content/images/tanning/2.jpg" alt="" />
					    <img src="/content/images/tanning/3.jpg" alt="" />
					    <img src="/content/images/tanning/4.jpg" alt="" />
					    <img src="/content/images/tanning/5.jpg" alt="" />
					    <img src="/content/images/tanning/6.jpg" alt="" />
					</div>
				</div>
			</div>
		</div>
	</div>
</div>

<script src="~/Scripts/jquery.nivo.slider.pack.js"></script>

<script type="text/javascript">
$(window).load(function() {
    $('#slider').nivoSlider({
        effect: 'random',
        directionNav: false,
        controlNav: false,
        controlNavThumbs: false,
        pauseOnHover: false
    });
});
</script>

